content.html: Rishi Sunak has been crowned our third Prime Minister in 7 weeks. Chosen by around 200 Tory MPs - less than 0.0003% of the public - in what became a contest with one candidate. He has no democratic mandate. We need a #GeneralElectionNow
content.value:
Rishi Sunak has been crowned our third Prime Minister in 7 weeks.

Chosen by around 200 Tory MPs - less than 0.0003% of the public - in what became a contest with one candidate.

He has no democratic mandate.

We need a #GeneralElectionNow
